  "created": "2025-10-15",
  "description": "Sulfur metabolism in E. coli assimilates inorganic sulfate or organic sulfur sources for cysteine and methionine biosynthesis. Sulfate is taken up by CysPUWA ABC transporter, activated to APS by CysD, reduced to sulfite by CysH, then to sulfide by CysIJ. Sulfide combines with O-acetylserine (from serine) via CysK/CysM to form cysteine. Alternative pathways use thiosulfate, sulfite, or organic sulfur. Regulation is via CysB activator responding to N-acetylserine.",
  "id": "ecoli_sulfur_metabolism",
  "keywords": [
    "sulfur metabolism",
    "cysteine biosynthesis",
    "sulfate assimilation",
    "CysK",
    "CysB"
  ],
  "lastUpdated": "2025-10-15",
  "logicGates": {
    "and": 3,
    "not": 5,
    "or": 3
  },
  "mermaid": "graph TD\n    %% Sulfur Source Selection\n    A[Sulfur Sources Available] --> B{OR: Which<br/>Sulfur Source?}\n    B -->|Preferred - Sulfate| C[SO4 2-]\n    B -->|Alternative - Thiosulfate| D[S2O3 2-]\n    B -->|Alternative - Sulfite| E[SO3 2-]\n    B -->|Organic - Cysteine| F[External Cysteine]\n    \n    %% Sulfate Uptake\n    C --> G[CysPUWA ABC Transporter]\n    G --> H{AND: ATP + Periplasmic<br/>Binding Protein?}\n    H -->|No| I[\\Uptake Blocked/]\n    H -->|Yes| J[Sulfate Transported]\n    J --> K[Cytoplasmic Sulfate]\n    \n    %% Sulfate Activation\n    K --> L[CysD ATP Sulfurylase]\n    L --> M[Sulfate + ATP]\n    M --> N[Adenosine 5'-Phosphosulfate APS]\n    N --> O[PPi Released]\n    \n    %% APS Reduction\n    O --> P[CysH APS Reductase]\n    P --> Q{AND: Thioredoxin<br/>Reduced?}\n    Q -->|No| R[\\Reduction Blocked/]\n    Q -->|Yes| S[APS \u2192 Sulfite + AMP]\n    S --> T[SO3 2-]\n    \n    %% Alternative Sulfite Entry\n    E --> U[Sulfite Transport]\n    U --> T\n    \n    %% Thiosulfate Branch\n    D --> V[Thiosulfate Reductase]\n    V --> W[S2O3 \u2192 SO3 + S2-]\n    W --> T\n    W --> X[Free Sulfide]\n    \n    %% Sulfite Reduction\n    T --> Y[CysIJ Sulfite Reductase]\n    Y --> Z{AND: NADPH + Siroheme<br/>Cofactor?}\n    Z -->|No| R\n    Z -->|Yes| AA[6 NADPH + SO3]\n    AA --> AB[Sulfide + H2O]\n    AB --> X\n    \n    %% O-Acetylserine Synthesis\n    AC(\\1) --> AD[SerA/SerB/SerC]\n    AD --> AE[Serine Availability]\n    AE --> AF[CysE Serine Acetyltransferase]\n    AF --> AG[Serine + Acetyl-CoA]\n    AG --> AH[O-Acetylserine OAS]\n    AH --> AI[/N-Acetylserine/]\n    \n    %% Cysteine Synthase Reaction\n    X --> AJ[Sulfide S2-]\n    AI --> AJ\n    AJ --> AK{OR: Which<br/>Synthase?}\n    AK -->|CysK - Major| AL[CysK O-Acetylserine Sulfhydrylase]\n    AK -->|CysM - Minor| AM[CysM O-Acetylserine Sulfhydrylase]\n    \n    AL --> AN[OAS + S2- \u2192 Cysteine]\n    AM --> AN\n    AN --> AO(\\1)\n    AO --> AP[Acetate Released]\n    \n    %% CysB Regulation\n    AI --> AQ[N-Acetylserine Accumulation]\n    AQ --> AR[/CysB Transcriptional Activator/]\n    AR --> AS[CysB Binds N-Acetylserine]\n    AS --> AT[CysB-DNA Complex]\n    AT --> AU[cys Operon Activation]\n    AU --> AV[CysPUWA/CysD/CysH/CysIJ Expression]\n    AV --> G\n    \n    %% Cysteine Utilization\n    AO --> AW{OR: Cysteine<br/>Fate?}\n    AW -->|Protein Synthesis| AX[tRNA-Cys Charging]\n    AW -->|Methionine Synthesis| AY[MetB/MetC Pathway]\n    AW -->|Iron-Sulfur Clusters| AZ[IscS Cysteine Desulfurase]\n    AW -->|Glutathione| BA[GSH Biosynthesis]\n    \n    %% Methionine Pathway\n    AY --> BB[Cystathionine Intermediate]\n    BB --> BC(\\1)\n    BC --> BD(\\1)\n    BD --> BE([Methionine Output])\n    \n    %% Fe-S Cluster Assembly\n    AZ --> BF[Sulfur Transfer]\n    BF --> BG[Fe-S Scaffold]\n    BG --> BH[Fe-S Cluster]\n    BH --> BI([Cofactor Production])\n    \n    %% Glutathione Synthesis\n    BA --> BJ[\u03b3-Glutamylcysteine]\n    BJ --> BK[Glutathione GSH]\n    BK --> BL([Antioxidant Defense])\n    \n    %% Protein Incorporation\n    AX --> BM[Ribosomal Translation]\n    BM --> BN[Cysteine in Proteins]\n    BN --> BO([Disulfide Bonds/Active Sites])\n    \n    %% Organic Sulfur Salvage\n    F --> BP[Dipeptide Uptake]\n    BP --> BQ[Peptidase Cleavage]\n    BQ --> AO\n    \n    %% Feedback Inhibition\n    AO --> BR[\"\\{AND: High Cysteine<br/>AND CysB?/\"]}\n    BR -->|No| AS\n    BR -->|Yes| BS[/CysB Feedback Inhibition/]\n    BS --> BT[\\cys Genes Repressed/]\n    BT --> BU([Balanced Synthesis])\n    \n    I --> BV([Sulfur Starvation])\n    R --> BV\n    \n    %% Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n    style B fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style A fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style C fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style D fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style E fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style F fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style G fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style H fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style I fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff\n    style J fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style K fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style L fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style M fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style N fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style O fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style P fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style Q fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style R fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff\n    style S fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style T fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style U fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style V fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style W fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style X fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style Y fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style Z fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AA fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AB fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AC fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AD fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AE fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AF fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AG fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AH fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AI fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AJ fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AK fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style AL fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AM fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AN fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AO fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AP fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AQ fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AR fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style AS fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AT fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AU fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AV fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AW fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style AX fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AY fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AZ fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BA fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style BB fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BC fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BD fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BE fill:#000000,color:#fff\n    style BF fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BG fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style